# Flutter Conventions

- Null-safe Dart; use `analysis_options.yaml` lints
- Feature logic in `lib/features/`; shared UI in `lib/shared/`; global services in `lib/core/`
- Player app: `lib/features/`; Admin app: `lib/modules/`
- Support dev, staging, production flavours — no hardcoded Firebase project IDs in feature code
- Do not write official leaderboard positions or final results from the client
- Localize user-facing strings; prepare for 23 languages from Version 1 architecture
